{
  "stem": "15396.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They, we couldn't have had a better time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were very pampered, in fact, by this lovely aunt.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and then we had an uncle who didn't marry either, then another uncle who did and had a nice family.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we stayed a lot in Greenville.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, when I was, when I was ready to graduate, I used to-- to make a living, I was wrestling, because I'd-- I left home.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because my uncle who was supporting us at that time and living somewhere else, but he wrote a letter saying, give up football and-- and be serious or else.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, I wouldn't-- no way on Earth I'd give up football, so I moved out that night.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then, I had various jobs, and I'd had tuberculosis when I was young, so I-- I got a paper route and I would run the entire distance to try and build up my lungs and-- and I started wrestling.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was another good way.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And by chance, I got into that professionally.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In-- Yes, and then I would use-- That's where I got the first name, Bob Wilson.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I would use that name sometimes so that you couldn't-- if you lost your amateur standing, you couldn't play football in school.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I had offers for scholarships to universities.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The minute they-- Then one day, stupidly, I let them take a picture of me and they found out I was wrestling professionally, and-- But that was the best thing ever happened to me, when I went off to, to school in Paris instead to study art.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very much so, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were-- They were-- As I say, my sisters were the pillars of the community, and very-- we-- I was an Episcopalian.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
